        <div class="feature-avatar"></div>
        <h4 class="feature-title">Eco-Delivery</h4>
        <p class="feature-para">An eco-friendly, reusable bag is left at your address each week on your delivery day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



